title: The Queen's Gambit - Ceiling Games (Piano Cover)
description:
What a series! So good. If you haven't watched it yet you should. I went through it in two days and I can't wait to watch it again. Everything, the story, the actors, the sets, the chess games and the music of course. Everything was amazing! There are so many great pieces of music from the soundtrack that I want to do a piano arrangement of all of them. Please let me know which ones are your favorites! I loved the concept of the chess board on the ceiling so I decided to start with that one. I hope you like it!
I play everything by ear so no sheets.
Thanks a lot for watching.
